Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.23,1:42:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Mhm. Um, see approval is associated with\Nsurvival.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.11,1:42:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the tribal culture of the wolf, the\Ndog pe without the approval of the pack,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.52,1:42:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you die. So, it brings up survival\Nreally. If you don't have anybody else's
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.67,1:42:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,approval, you won't survive.\NTherefore, you got to risk death by
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.28,1:42:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,letting it go.\NYou're not afraid of dying, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.84,1:42:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that one up right now. This minute.\N>> I think I'm more afraid of the uh
