Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.15,1:42:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So then the approval would be uh looking\Nfor assurance, looking for agreement. Uh
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.88,1:42:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's pride in a way, isn't it?\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.84,1:42:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Wanting people like you. So it's coming\Nfrom lack.
