Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.08,1:43:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't know what elite is. If you wanted\Nthe slightest thing from any of them,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.15,1:43:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you were you automatically out. You had\Nto be completely self-sufficient. If
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.19,1:43:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you're looking for a connection, they\Njust got it like this. and you didn't
