Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.63,1:43:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,total and complete within yourself.\NEven if you have nothing at all, then uh
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.71,1:43:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing is to be content with nothing\Nat all. Nothing at all is a wonderful
