Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.71,1:43:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To have nothing at all, very hard to\Nachieve it. Try it. See how hard it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.84,1:43:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody screams and hollers. The\Nfamily says you've gone insane. you
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.04,1:43:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,know,\Ngave it all away, walked away from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.60,1:44:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lost his mind. That's true.\NYou see, you can't come from lack. That
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.28,1:44:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which you are is already complete and\Ntotal. It doesn't need anything. Just
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.92,1:44:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,thinks it does.\NIt's because it thinks it does. It feels
