Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.96,1:44:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just becoming from a belief system.\NAnd so you have to have the courage to
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.67,1:44:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,drop it.\N>> All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.19,1:44:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And everybody may say you're stupid and\Nlost your mind. That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.92,1:44:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thanks.\N>> Tell them my my doctor says that I'm
